caption:
Outstanding. 

I recently reviewed this Porsche Panamera Turbo S E-Hybrid 🔥 It might cost almost £200k and weigh 2.3 tons, but WHAT a machine! 

Under the bonnet you will find a 4L Twin Turbo V8 mated to a beautifully calibrated hybrid system, giving this car a total combined output of 782hp and 1000nm, It managed 0-60 in under 2.6 seconds and will do over 200mph! 

The complex active air suspension was my personal highlight, it meant this luxurious rocket ship had an outstanding ride quality and handling true to it's Porsche badge.

This is German engineering and technology at its absolute best, if only they still made the Sport Turismo version. 

Full Review on my channel 🎬

#porsche #porschepanamera #panamera #panameraturbos #german

caption:
Older Cars Are Amazing! (When maintained) 

My friends at @elitegarages let me drive their 2011 BMW 320d out to @bmwclassic in Munich & celebrate the car covering 250000 miles, that's more than ten times around the world 🤯

During this road trip we tested real life mpg, 0-60 times and a top speed run on the wonderful German Autobahn 👀

Huge thanks to Elite Garages, BMW Classic, @michelinuk for a set of Cross Climate 3's and  @josh_whittemore ❤️

#bmw #elitegarages #michelin
